  "title": "SALES ASSISTANT MANAGER",
  "description": "<h2>Job Summary</h2><p>The Sales Assistant Manager supports the Store Manager in driving sales performance, managing daily store operations, and leading the sales team to deliver excellent customer service. This role plays a key part in achieving sales targets and maintaining brand standards in a mobile phone retail environment.</p><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Assist the Store Manager in overseeing daily store operations and sales activities</p></li><li><p>Drive mobile phone and accessory sales to achieve individual and store targets</p></li><li><p>Support, train, and motivate sales staff to improve product knowledge and sales skills</p></li><li><p>Ensure excellent customer service and handle customer inquiries, complaints, and after-sales issues</p></li><li><p>Monitor inventory levels, stock display, and merchandising standards</p></li><li><p>Prepare sales reports and provide performance feedback to the Store Manager</p></li><li><p>Implement promotional campaigns and ensure correct execution in-store</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with company policies, procedures, and retail standards</p></li></ul><h2>Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Diploma or Bachelor’s degree in Business, Retail Management, or related field preferred</p></li><li><p>2–4 years of retail sales experience, preferably in mobile phones or consumer electronics</p></li><li><p>Previous experience in a supervisory or assistant manager role is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Strong sales mindset with proven ability to meet or exceed targets</p></li><li><p>Good leadership, communication, and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Customer-oriented, proactive, and able to work under pressure</p></li><li><p>Willing to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays</p></li></ul><h2>What We Offer</h2><ul><li><p>Competitive basic salary + sales commission</p></li><li><p>Clear career progression to Store Manager</p></li><li><p>Product training on latest mobile devices and technology</p></li><li><p>Supportive and fast-paced retail working environment</p></li></ul>",
